<lb ed="W" n="0215a14"/><lg xml:id="lgW06p0215a1401" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:4em">於湛精明既不通，</l><l rend="text-indent:0em">狂花亂發遍空中<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0215001" n="0215001"/>。</l>
<lb ed="W" n="0215a15"/><l rend="text-indent:4em">根塵互遣亡纖翳，</l><l rend="text-indent:0em">法喻重宣有異功。</l>
<lb ed="W" n="0215a16"/><l rend="text-indent:4em">左右各牽<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0215002" n="0215002"/>迷至理，</l><l rend="text-indent:0em">是非鋒起入凡籠。</l>
<lb ed="W" n="0215a17"/><l rend="text-indent:4em">結心解處俱分散，</l><l rend="text-indent:0em">焰焰金烏出海東。</l></lg></cb:div>
