<lb ed="W" n="0216a09"/><lg xml:id="lgW06p0216a0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:4em">一念初萌萬仞高，</l><l rend="text-indent:0em">含藏八識自堅牢。</l>
<lb ed="W" n="0216a10"/><l rend="text-indent:4em">豫且網內應難免，</l><l rend="text-indent:0em">地藏珠中豈可逃？</l>
<lb ed="W" n="0216a11"/><l rend="text-indent:4em">六類紛紛俱繫綴，</l><l rend="text-indent:0em">四生浩浩共煎熬。</l>
<lb ed="W" n="0216a12"/><l rend="text-indent:4em">奢摩他體能端的，</l><l rend="text-indent:0em">彼此相忘入聖曹。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="W" n="0216a13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">楞嚴心印咒　(至)解冤結真言</cb:mulu><head>楞嚴心印咒　<note place="inline">至</note>解冤結真言</head>
